{"tid":273517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國的問題，主要是中共的問題，還是中國的問題?","createTime":"2017-06-06T15:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T05:33:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1130659b437306a206078db879f3c9f62df091","tid":273517,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"跟一資深中國通對聊。<br />\n<br />\n我問:「中國的問題，主要是中共的問題，還是中國的問題?」<br />\n他答:「是中國的問題。」<br />\n我問:「許多人是反共而不反中，你怎樣看?」<br />\n他答:「因為若反中，隨時生計也有困難，而反共仍可甚至可能有助搵食。」"},{"pid":"8cd2bd25777aada797de79215fbd37bba40ec58a","tid":273517,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨係由中國人組成，所以，問題的根源是中國人有問題"},{"pid":"b2b20ac53fb0ea595685c75e03d6300b90057ffd","tid":273517,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"因為中國人係低劣民族，這是事實，但所有中國人都不願意面對更盡量去掩飾，這才是最大的問題。"},{"pid":"f2d1aeb866b06f5ea304fe5506555c7d3108f3f7","tid":273517,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"中共，只不過是把中國人的本性舒發出來"},{"pid":"95287d8e96b6da96fca1ebdc31de41942c2aa661","tid":273517,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"乜7都賴落政府到<br />\nD平民咪又係壞事做盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ab826872c1222591c3546679f7da7b40501ecb","tid":273517,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5304eb7c356bd4613bb8a650f5cc890fd4a73c88","tid":273517,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"我直頭反華"},{"pid":"4823d406e93efb45e24a6e7f27f2d5a03d2dad43","tid":273517,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"以前：<br />\n中共殺死了中國<br />\n現在：<br />\n中共成為了中國，等於中國。<br />\n<br />\n中共問題